MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: TutorialGuided_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 55d80ac21c79dd14f8e1397ca6e4b64d, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 2578400000000012
    m_Localized: Tutorial complete. You are ready for the main game. A fresh factory
      will begin when you continue.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665243
    m_Localized: Advance time until at least one day passes, then check whether your
      resources were sold. Resources are sold every day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665241
    m_Localized: Press the close button at the top right of the market panel to go
      back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665240
    m_Localized: Use the minus button to sell the premium wood you produced.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665239
    m_Localized: Press the Market button on the left to open the market panel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000011
    m_Localized: Now it is time to sell what you produced and earn a profit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665238
    m_Localized: "While time runs, watch the resource panel on the right. Advance
      time until at least one day passes\u2014you will see resources move, produce,
      and get consumed."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665232
    m_Localized: Press the Start button to run the factory clock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665230
    m_Localized: Running the factory takes time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665237
    m_Localized: Now let's run the factory.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665235
    m_Localized: Next, click the Sawmill and assign the 'Premium Wood' resource.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665234
    m_Localized: Each building must specify what resource it outputs. Click the Unload
      building you placed and use the resource selection button to assign 'Raw Wood'.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000010
    m_Localized: Place the Load building on the grid, directly to the right of the
      last road tile you placed. Any facing is fine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000009
    m_Localized: Select the Load building. It receives goods from your factory and
      sends them to storage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665229
    m_Localized: Place one road tile next to the Sawmill, to the right.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665228
    m_Localized: Select the Road tool again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000006
    m_Localized: Place the Sawmill on the grid, right next to the road and facing
      right.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000005
    m_Localized: Select the Sawmill. It processes raw wood into premium wood.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665227
    m_Localized: Place one road tile next to the Unload building, to the right.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665226
    m_Localized: Select the Road tool to connect the Unload building.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665233
    m_Localized: Yellow arrows show the next grid cell where resources will move.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000004
    m_Localized: Place the Unload building on the grid, facing right.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000003
    m_Localized: Select the Unload building. It sends resources from storage into
      your factory.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665225
    m_Localized: Press the Start button to advance time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000002
    m_Localized: Pantory is a game where resources move over time. You can advance
      time from the time control panel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665242
    m_Localized: Well done! As time passes, raw wood will be added to storage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000001
    m_Localized: Use the plus button on the Logging Camp to add another logging camp.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665216
    m_Localized: Now let's build a production line for premium wood and get the factory
      running.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30820150800695296
    m_Localized: Every factory needs staff, and managing employee morale is very
      important.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30819995552727040
    m_Localized: Pantory has a convenient auto employee assignment feature. It is
      enabled by default.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000016
    m_Localized: First, learn the controls. Drag the mouse or use WASD to move the
      camera, and scroll the mouse wheel to zoom.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000015
    m_Localized: A practice road is in the top-left of the map. Move to the top-left
      and click the practice road on the grid to remove it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000014
    m_Localized: Turn on the Removal Mode switch.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000013
    m_Localized: Let's learn removal mode. A practice road is placed at the top-left
      of the map. Removal mode lets you delete buildings and roads.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665236
    m_Localized: The Load station accepts any resource, so it does not need an assignment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2578400000000000
    m_Localized: Welcome to the tutorial. You will place Logging Camp, Unload, Sawmill,
      and Load, then connect them with roads.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821035190665421
    m_Localized: Expanding production lines is not much different from what you just
      did. You can connect different production lines together or split them apart.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30821036190665226
    m_Localized: As time passes, you will see raw wood appear in storage. Let's advance
      one day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2160556255887360
    m_Localized: Well done! Now turn off the Removal Mode switch.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2191034279149568
    m_Localized: After selecting a building, use the Q and E keys or the rotate buttons
      at the bottom right to rotate it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2201319677247488
    m_Localized: Here you can see how many resources to sell to the market each day.
      Negative values mean sell; positive values mean buy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2273495235313664
    m_Localized: Use this button to check your current income and expenses. Stay
      in the black and run your factory steadily!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
